{"tid":1738251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【黎明行動】必定係損人不利己既行動","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:53.000Z","uid":209382,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac1a1d26b0bc7f74c6e19ddee6b8720bad13d77","tid":1738251,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"黎明行動，每次行動都無得到民心，得到既只係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大量藍絲既攻擊</span></span></span>，同埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">市民既埋怨</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n前幾次行動，肯定已經有黃絲/企我地個邊既市民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感到模糊</span></span><br />\n唸下每一次既黎明行動，我地會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得到D咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續漫無目的地搞黎明行動，只會令市民對非建制派失去更多信心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明理大事件，大家好灰，好嬲，好唔甘心，竟然可以咁樣比狗冼左一獲。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">令自己被仇恨支配，場運動最後必會凶多吉少</span><br />\n<br />\n【政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。...我仍希望你們能夠明白：本著對香港的熱愛，你們已展現了無比的勇氣，改寫了香港的歷史。當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。】梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日希望勇武靜落黎，琴日poly一戰，大家都好累，呢幾日交比和理非，希望大家用剩低既日子，<span style=\"color: red;\">好好反思，好好整文宣，同埋好好咁迎接區選！！</span><br />\n<br />\n最後我覺得大家需要做既係，不時聽一聽正反意見，特別係對家既言論，唔係完全接受對家言論，係將對家言論好好分析，<span style=\"color: red;\">望下自己今次既過錯並接受佢，我相信呢樣野係唔易做，但有陣時要放一放低自己，改過今次過錯，之後既行動先會有進步。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有巴打都出過類似既post，加上蕭生呢條片，希望大家好好參詳。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738116/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jUGIEKovV2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjUGIEKovV2Q&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=5eb10831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jUGIEKovV2Q</a>"},{"pid":"22e0ff5f7eac141d20e4509f6901daab2889f001","tid":1738251,"uid":193380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"[1119] 五毛新風向：今日冇黎明行動，以後唔再塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737615</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KkE4suw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKkE4suw.png&h=fe34cdd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b4fd47a4eeedc5dfccd250be65e809e99bfc199","tid":1738251,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"251c9c481a68062ca118c088b538a78947f0d732","tid":1738251,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:48:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"81b57a6f8acc8f32572e804b397f58681b6a7060","tid":1738251,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1737420/page/1?post=9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1737420/page/1?post=9</a><br />\n[真檢討］再係咁樣 香港人係行唔到落去<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c53098174bf2f479dd8cc78b3d41a2cf8555e075","tid":1738251,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEiwqcy_a5U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEiwqcy_a5U&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=36692f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEiwqcy_a5U</a>"},{"pid":"5eb7eabbdb8ec357d727a4630a34f0